data.description: Incredible Estate Home in a perfect setting. HERE is your dream home in the suburbs.  NO HOA,  NO CDD - Privacy and security yet only minutes from the city in the highly coveted Steinbrenner School district. This estate home has a gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances wood cabinets and granite counter tops. A formal living room plus spacious family room that overlooks pond and conservation in addition to very large and well landscaped yard. Large screened in pool/spa with large lanai. Plenty of room for entertaining friends and family. Located on a gently winding tree-lined street. This incredible estate home is two minutes from the veterans Expressway and has Carrollwood, Northdale, and Citrus Park only minutes away. Must see! Square footage(s) and lot size of home taken from public records. Buyer is advised to verify.    Large Rustic Mediterranean Tile and   Crown Moulding throughout the living areas.   Hurricane Protection installed and available for all the Windows.  Large Fenced in Dog Run.  72” TV in the Family Room Conveys,  Pool Table and Light Conveys,  Washer and Dryer Convey.   15KW Whole House Generator Included
